      "text": "Done — the characters are now defined with stable visual and behavioral anchors.\n\nLocked in:\n- **Panda** — gentle, vulnerable, classic giant panda look, no wardrobe, slightly slouched and introspective\n- **Psychologist** — calm professional woman, neat dark hair, muted neutral wardrobe, warm but precise presence\n\nI also turned both into clean reference-ready character sheet prompts, so the next step is to generate those two character images and check that they feel consistent and usable for the film."
