      "id": "user-1774457368028-8ljy0s",
      "role": "user",
      "text": "Scene: Minimal therapy room. Clean comedic rhythm. Short.\n\nShot 1 — Medium wide. A panda lies on a therapy couch. The psychiatrist sits beside him, partially cropped at frame edge.\nDialogue (Panda): \"Doctor, everyone hates me. Either because of my black side or my white side.\"\n\nShot 2 — Medium. The psychiatrist sips from his mug, then sets it down. No dialogue.\n\nShot 3 — Close-up. The doctor asks:\nDialogue (Doctor): \"And which one do you like better?\"\n\nShot 4 — Medium close-up. The panda responds with strong, desperate gestures.\nDialogue (Panda): \"Neither.\"\n\nShot 5 — Medium close-up tightening to close-up, slow dolly-in toward the doctor. He looks up from his notes and adjusts his glasses.\nDialogue (Doctor): \"Then that's where we start.\""
